column4: NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "492188474E5B6796B01E1E874CF63304", "Rest as much as possible. That\'s the key to your Digimon\'s health.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "1CFB31004CD70AC7F5A5B6B9D0DB5B56", "Alright. Let me tell you how the city will grow and prosper...")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "5D9BEA8A4B0CE0097645C5B8BD7C6E14", "When a Rookie Digimon comes to the city, it\'s plus one point.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "11DBD1704B6CC098F5332BBAB9896CC0", "And when a Champion Digimon comes to the city, it\'s plus two points.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "0EBCB3984A2188CBAA860EB93A2EEC33", "If an Ultimate Digimon comes to the city, it\'s plus three points.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "B04ACF684E24D6C9A6CEC8B7270792C1", "However, there are three Champion Digimon that are not very useful.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "0B48293E45CAF9C2358D32919B18C224", "When one of them comes, it\'s only plus one point.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "1CB1E1F9410090DD500F52BF38B8EDED", "Let me tell you a little bit about Types.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "0B471DF24A4CBA4AF76D87A82B671E1E", "If an opponent is the same Type as your Digimon partner, he may not battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "064929DD4C5E6EA2D312AEA13CBCD228", "And if your Digimon\'s Type is not compatible, he can be refused at a door.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "E20847FD4CED5773B06DD2A280107307", "Other than that, maybe you don\'t have to worry about it.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "5D112E8644FC3B8278F899BCE5845ED1", "Let me tell you about Tamer Level.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "81DD4B97431C48CAA34301BAA1851A87", "Tamer Level will increase if you can raise Digimon to Ultimate Digimon.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "95CB1BAB45905CA32B2814BFEF6603E5", "And winning a championship in a high level tournament is very good.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "D36E76C94CF855E0BA92279B248701A8", "It will go up naturally. You don\'t have to worry about it too much.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "5B1F23384421A8EEA92CFC82145FCABE", "On the other hand, you have to pay attention not to let it go down.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "383A1CF94252D0294E426D886817BFAA", "If your Digimon fades away, your Tamer Level will go down for sure.")
NSLOCTEXT("[0B15C8A74E53A0BF1440E6AD5D96DB12]", "65EE7FBA49C74E4DF080738F90457DAC", "If you regularly have care mistakes, it might go down. Be careful.")
